===Season 2 (2015)===
On October 17, 2015, all episodes of season 2, along with the previous season, were made available for streaming on USA's website, as well as via the On Demand service on many cable systems.<ref>{{Cite web|title = Videos {{!}} Satisfaction|url = http://www.usanetwork.com/satisfaction/videos| website = USA Network|accessdate = 2015-10-25}}</ref>

